---
layout: base.njk
title: About Mitria
permalink: /about/
---

<section class="hero hero--short">
  <img src="{{ about.heroImage }}" alt="About Mitria" class="hero__image" fetchpriority="high" loading="eager">
  <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero__content"><h1>About Mitria</h1></div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__text">
        <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
        <h2>{{ about.storyHeading }}</h2>
        {{ about.storyText1 | md | safe }}
        {{ about.storyText2 | md | safe }}
        {{ about.storyText3 | md | safe }}
      </div>
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="{{ about.storyImage }}" alt="Friends hiking through the highlands">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="star-divider"><img src="/images/star2.svg" alt=""></div>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__text">
        <span class="section-label">What We Do</span>
        <h2>How we work</h2>
        <div class="about-intro">{{ about.whatWeDoText | md | safe }}</div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">Mitria operates as a social enterprise. We're a registered business that functions like a nonprofit: over 80% of profits fund Project Zomia and the community projects it supports.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="{{ pageSettings.aboutHowWeWorkImage }}" alt="How we work">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="what-we-do-grid">
      <div class="what-we-do-item"><img src="/images/star2.svg" alt="" class="what-we-do-icon"><div><h4>Trip Leading</h4><p>Custom-tailored experiences with local guides and community hosts.</p></div></div>
      <div class="what-we-do-item"><img src="/images/star2.svg" alt="" class="what-we-do-icon"><div><h4>Community Projects</h4><p>Infrastructure, conservation, cultural, and education initiatives.</p></div></div>
      <div class="what-we-do-item"><img src="/images/star2.svg" alt="" class="what-we-do-icon"><div><h4>Custom Itineraries</h4><p>We build tailored travel plans for individuals and groups.</p></div></div>
      <div class="what-we-do-item"><img src="/images/star2.svg" alt="" class="what-we-do-icon"><div><h4>Volunteer Placement</h4><p>Connecting people with ethical organizations that need support.</p></div></div>
      <div class="what-we-do-item"><img src="/images/star2.svg" alt="" class="what-we-do-icon"><div><h4>Social Activism</h4><p>Advocating for ethical elephant tourism and mahout welfare.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="commitments-section">
  <div class="commitments-bg" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85f82e?w=1600&q=80');"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h2>Our Commitments</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="commitments-grid">
      <div class="commitment-card"><h4>No Poverty Tourism</h4><p>Our experiences will always be dignified, consent-based interactions facilitated by community members. Any and all donations are given to community leaders to be distributed as they see fit. We do not allow visitors to give sweets or gifts to local children.</p></div>
      <div class="commitment-card"><h4>Community-Led Approach</h4><p>Community members decide what's needed and local voices guide all projects, experiences, and funding.</p></div>
      <div class="commitment-card"><h4>Animal Welfare</h4><p>No riding, bathing, or close-contact with elephants, ever. Same goes for all animals unless the experience is strictly vetted by our team or a third-party organization.</p></div>
      <div class="commitment-card"><h4>Environmental Consciousness</h4><p>We're committed to low-impact travel, single-use plastic reduction, and always having an emphasis on supporting conservation initiatives.</p></div>
      <div class="commitment-card"><h4>Local Economy First</h4><p>We prioritize local suppliers, guides, artisans, and skilled workers. You won't be teaching English or doing anything that should be done by a qualified local on our trips.</p></div>
      <div class="commitment-card"><h4>Genuine Experiences</h4><p>We don't force good feelings by staging community interaction or lying to you about your impact. We're upfront about where your money goes and why.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="star-divider"><img src="/images/star2.svg" alt=""></div>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading"><span class="section-label">Our Friends</span><h2>Partners doing good work</h2></div>
    <div class="partner-grid">
      {% for partner in partners.partners %}
      <a href="{{ partner.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner-grid__card">
        <div class="partner-grid__image">
          <img src="{{ partner.image }}" alt="{{ partner.name }}">
        </div>
        <div class="partner-grid__text">
          <h4>{{ partner.name }}</h4>
          <p>{{ partner.description }}</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="partners-cta">
      <a href="/countries/" class="btn--text">Explore our country pages for more partners and good folks to visit</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
